    "difficulty": "medium",
    "sourceYear": 2024,
    "en": {
      "question": "A father is 30 years older than his son. After 5 years, the father will be 3 times as old as his son. What is the present age of the son?",
      "options": [
        "10 years",
        "12 years",
        "15 years",
        "18 years"
      ],
      "explanation": "Let son's age = x. Father's age = x + 30. After 5 years: (x+30+5) = 3(x+5). x+35 = 3x+15. 2x=20, x=10."
    },
    "hi": {
      "question": "एक पिता अपने पुत्र से 30 वर्ष बड़ा है। 5 वर्ष बाद, पिता की आयु पुत्र की आयु की 3 गुनी होगी। पुत्र की वर्तमान आयु क्या है?",
      "options": [
        "10 वर्ष",
        "12 वर्ष",
        "15 वर्ष",
        "18 वर्ष"
      ],
      "explanation": "माना पुत्र की आयु = x। पिता की आयु = x + 30। 5 वर्ष बाद: (x+30+5) = 3(x+5)। x+35 = 3x+15। 2x=20, x=10।"
    }
  },
